but really understand what they had to be grateful for.

78
00:03:12.464 --> 00:03:13.684
And this was huge,

79
00:03:13.684 --> 00:03:16.404
I mean this was probably the major difference that I saw

80
00:03:16.404 --> 00:03:20.289
in the attitudes of children

